{"tid":1071166,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(圖)MTR應該轉用運輸帶代替路軌","createTime":"2019-03-21T07:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T09:39:36.000Z","uid":90183,"like":41,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2d752f5d767c5bbec531b238b6acc4f58102b077","tid":1071166,"uid":90183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"見到有人提出轉做成條路軌都係車卡 或者 轉做運輸帶<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1070873/page/5\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1070873/page/5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFOt5tq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFOt5tq.jpg&h=23c1e4c4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如上圖  月台上慢線先 趕時間可轉線至中線再去快線<br />\n就黎到自己要去嘅站就預早由快線轉去中線再慢線返上月台走人<br />\n<br />\nreference: 電梯分3種速度 按人流量而定<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170402/bkn-20170402045942889-0402_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170402%2Fbkn-20170402045942889-0402_00822_001.html&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3Dw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=e19975d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170402/bkn-20170402045942889-0402_00822_001.html</a><br />\n雖然話宜家電梯每秒0.75米<br />\n但對於趕返工返學嘅一眾港豬  要上每秒2.78米(10km/hr)嘅運輸帶 其實並唔難<br />\n<br />\n既然垃圾MTR成日都壞車 真係俾人係運輸帶上面行或者趕時間跑仲好<br />\n平時係中環去香港站個電梯跑其實都好撚快<br />\n<br />\n1. 可以防止人跳軌<br />\n2. 隨時乘搭運輸帶就得 唔需要等車到<br />\n3. 大家一齊無關愛座 廢老驚就企慢線<br />\n4. 更換零件相對容易<br />\n5. 唔需要咩通訊系統 <br />\n6. 成本較低 <br />\n7. 炒撚晒d廢物波板糖人 (唔需要小心車門阻人上車)<br />\n8. 炒撚晒車長<br />\n9. 運作時間可延長"},{"pid":"ad800b467a6f2cc34d5dcce3bac3921649492e47","tid":1071166,"uid":44646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:09:47.000Z","msg":"Asimov有本小說有類似概念"},{"pid":"e979a9c685d4e9ad8806f2d05511def7bb26dc9f","tid":1071166,"uid":102681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"wall e"},{"pid":"94ea49f226b13542b94f79d2423bfb542b349955","tid":1071166,"uid":90183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1939/d1939901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1939%2Fd1939901.jpg&h=4ea2598f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意圖<br />\n例如金鐘往海洋公園 3線上斜亦無難度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7e9n5Ymwz7k/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F7e9n5Ymwz7k%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=84c622a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔止月台   全tunnel牆身都可以加廣告增加收入"},{"pid":"9915b84601392df8dc04d109b5fe4910f3b6b78b","tid":1071166,"uid":7763,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"咁你有計過要掘幾深?"},{"pid":"09aedd0456c617addf548f654b79d01dacb2e627","tid":1071166,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"蝗仔痾篤尿就收你皮"},{"pid":"79d46db52d19eb7e09cfb3b4156934a234679e73","tid":1071166,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"運輸帶一樣會壞同炒埋一疊"},{"pid":"3917f47ef513c3cfec9270262859263bbd7667aa","tid":1071166,"uid":90183,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://kabk.github.io/go-theses-18-eliza-glukhova/img/flow.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkabk.github.io%2Fgo-theses-18-eliza-glukhova%2Fimg%2Fflow.gif&h=e9dc8553&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aed7cbace64a068660065627bd4d57e8f1019778","tid":1071166,"uid":43737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"同中國接軌,運輸帶都可以壞.<br />\n朗豪坊事件"},{"pid":"1b3ad090f475470f6a811c60e0a522880a074aaa","tid":1071166,"uid":90183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79d46db52d19eb7e09cfb3b4156934a234679e73","tid":1071166,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"運輸帶一樣會壞同炒埋一疊"