get=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/200811/%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%9F%E5%BE%9733km-h-5%E5%80%8B%E4%BD%A0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 地鐵四綫（即觀塘綫、荃灣線、港島綫、將軍澳綫）的平均車速，只有33km/h  ((所以運輸帶快線上30km/h 其實唔會比宜家速度慢太多   起碼唔需要被阻閂門d仆街阻開車))<br />\n2. 東鐵就快少少，平均車速有50km/h<br />\n3. 東涌綫同機場快綫，平均車速高達80km/h ((運輸帶比起呢兩條線就相對教慢))"},{"pid":"991af69ed262b7dbb20a94579fcf039d3ff19be0","tid":1071166,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"你比幾蚊<br />\n唔好咁多要求"},{"pid":"daa14a4797b5cff92fdac216c12772c37f58f50a","tid":1071166,"uid":90183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33c25be77f20a8e851f37ef02b6ecd9f9fa5f014","tid":1071166,"uid":114449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"點樣轉線？隨時可以轉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"隨時轉 <br />\n<br />\n運輸帶上面裝設與各線運輸帶同步速度嘅 吊環扶手<br />\n快線右面加設圍邊嘅扶手"},{"pid":"0687bdd9c71c64641b0c4a7f370e7167e018a6da","tid":1071166,"uid":70085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"其實10km/h 都幾快, 廢老應該上唔到. 同埋實全部人去曬快線, 變咗中慢線只會用嚟做過渡.而且要確保上面無靜止嘅嘢, 30km/h就算磨牆都好傷"},{"pid":"d523e1f4c0f8dc481de74fb3bf1e474f1b79eb6b","tid":1071166,"uid":19947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我腦海會出左迴轉壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}